Sentencas: Here we report a solid oxide electrolysis cell (SOEC) employing impregnated electrodes.
Titulo: High performance solid oxide electrolysis cell with impregnated electrodes

Sentencas: The cell structure consisted of a porous 430 L metal support, a Ni-Ce0.8Sm0.2O2-delta (SDC) impregnated 430 L-zirconia stabilized zirconia (YSZ) hydrogen electrode, a scandia stabilized zirconia (SSZ) electrolyte and a Nd2O3-Nd2NiO4+delta (Nd2O3-NNO) impregnated SSZ oxygen electrode.
Titulo: High performance solid oxide electrolysis cell with impregnated electrodes

Sentencas: The cell is prepared by tape casting, co-firing and impregnation techniques.
Titulo: High performance solid oxide electrolysis cell with impregnated electrodes

Sentencas: At an applied voltage of 1.3 V and 50% steam content, current density of 2.05 A cm(-2) is obtained at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: High performance solid oxide electrolysis cell with impregnated electrodes

Sentencas: The effect of the variation of H2O/H-2 ratio (3/97 to 70/30) on electrolysis performance at 750 degrees C is evaluated and the long-term stability in electrolysis mode is also investigated.
Titulo: High performance solid oxide electrolysis cell with impregnated electrodes
